{
  "stem": "27759.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then see, they gave us these uniforms that was supposed to have been impregnated.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in spite of the pregnation of the uniform, I was drenched to my skin.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And before we got to the bivouac area where we were going to bivouac that night, we had to march 15 miles inland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when we got to this bivouac area, you couldn't strike a match or nothing at night for fear that a German plane would spot it and bomb the area.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Or come down and strafe the area, whichever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- so I just took my tent shelter half--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- see, they put two soldiers together in each squad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one carried half of the tent shelter, and the other one carried the other half.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they reach a bivouac area, they'll take the two halves and put them together.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I just took my half and rolled up in it on the ground.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was soaked to my skin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then, the next morning, we got up and built a big bonfire.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Tried to dry our clothing out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I dried my clothing out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there was-- oh, that was my new-- the conditions under which I had to sleep.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As we advanced, I slept on the ground where it was snow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Or tried to sleep.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, just rest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In the snow, rain, whatever the weather conditions were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's as we advanced.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the first-- see, our outfit was attached.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were called-- referred to as Combat Services Supply.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "978.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we went in-- we were attached to the different divisions.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When we went in on Omaha Beach, we were attached to the Rangers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Rangers were made up of hardened criminals.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
